## Frontend Dashboard Design

### Dark theme, polished luxury feel вЂ” 3 main views:

**1. Dashboard Home**
- Top stats bar: Total Products | Brands Active | Items In Stock | Last Scrape Time
- Brand cards grid вЂ” each card shows: brand logo/name, product count, last scrape time, "Scrape Now" button with loading spinner
- "Scrape All" master button

**2. Products View**
- Filterable data table: Brand, Product Name, Category, Price, Colors, Sizes, Stock Status
- Search bar with live filtering
- Color chips showing available colors
- Stock badges (green = in stock, red = out of stock)
- Click row to expand and see all variant details
- Export button (CSV / Excel dropdown)

**3. Scrape History**
- Timeline of past scrape jobs with status, duration, products scraped
- Error details for failed scrapes

