## Implementation Order

We will build in this order to always have something testable:

1. **Backend skeleton** вЂ” FastAPI app, config, database models, migrations
2. **Anti-detection utilities** вЂ” UA rotation, delays, proxy support
3. **Base scraper** вЂ” Abstract class with shared logic
4. **First 2 scrapers** вЂ” On Running + Hourglass (one shoes, one cosmetics вЂ” to validate the architecture works across categories)
5. **API endpoints** вЂ” All REST endpoints
6. **Frontend dashboard** вЂ” Full UI with all 3 views
7. **Remaining 4 scrapers** вЂ” Hoka, Acne Studios, Maison Margiela, Drunk Elephant
8. **Export feature** вЂ” CSV/Excel export
9. **Polish** вЂ” Error handling, loading states, edge cases

