2. **Dashboard loads** вЂ” Verify all 6 brand cards appear with correct names/logos
3. **Trigger scrape** вЂ” Click "Scrape Now" on On Running, verify:
   - Loading spinner appears
   - Products populate the table after completion
   - Each product shows name, price, colors, sizes, stock status
4. **Filters work** вЂ” Filter by brand, search by product name, filter by stock status
5. **Export works** вЂ” Click Export CSV, open the file, verify data matches the dashboard
6. **Scrape history** вЂ” View scrape history, verify completed job appears with correct stats

> [!NOTE]
> Since scraping live websites is inherently flaky (sites change layouts, rate limits kick in), the first run of each scraper may need adjustments. We'll build and test iteratively вЂ” 2 scrapers first, then the remaining 4.

